# Cards

## Dashboard Metric Cards
- Payments: `bg-[#F5FBFE]`, Settlement: `bg-[#F0FDF4]`, Refunds: `bg-[#FEF2F2]`
- Shape: `rounded-[20px]`, padding: `p-5`
- Layout: `flex flex-col gap-3`
- Divider: `border-t border-border pt-3`

## Action Cards
- P0 (High Priority): `bg-[#ffebef]/60`, hover: `hover:bg-[#ffebef]`
- P1 (Low Priority): `bg-[#fff8e1]/60`, hover: `hover:bg-[#fff8e1]`
- No border/stroke, `rounded-lg`, `p-4`, `transition-colors`
- Icon on right side

## Notification Cards
- BG: `bg-[#fafafa]` (read), `bg-[#F5F9FE]` (unread)
- Shape: `rounded-[16px]`, padding: `p-[16px]`
- Hover: `hover:bg-accent/50`
- Unread indicator: `bg-primary size-2` blue dot

## Summary Cards (Payments page)

### Layout
- Flex strip: `flex items-center gap-1`
- Each card: `flex-1 rounded-[12px] p-5 flex flex-col`

### Card Colors
| Type | Background |
|---|---|
| Collections | `bg-[#eaf2fd]` |
| Adjustments | `bg-[#fdeeee]` |
| Deductions | `bg-[rgba(235,87,87,0.1)]` |
| Settlement Processed | `bg-[rgba(39,174,95,0.1)]` |
| Available for Settlement | `bg-[#e0f5fd]` |

### Card Content
- Label: `text-[14px] text-[#7e7e7e]`
- Amount: `text-[20px] font-semibold text-[#101010]`
- Link: `text-[12px] text-[#004299] font-medium hover:underline` with divider above

### Operator Symbols (16×16, `shrink-0`)
- Minus: single 2px×8px bar
- Equals: two 1.33px×8px bars, `gap-[2px]`
- Plus: cross of 1.33px bars

## Feature / Service Cards
- Container: `bg-white border border-[#e0e0e0] rounded-[12px] p-5 flex flex-col gap-4`
- Hover: `hover:bg-[#f5f9fe]`
- Icon: `size-10 rounded-[8px] bg-[#e0f5fd]`
- Title: `text-[14px] font-semibold text-[#101010]`
- Body: `text-[12px] text-[#7e7e7e] leading-[18px]`
- CTA: Secondary button with `ArrowRight` (`size-3.5`)
- Status chip: `px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-[12px] font-semibold`
- Grid: `grid grid-cols-2 gap-6`

## Device Cards (My Services)
- Container: `bg-white border border-[#e0e0e0] rounded-[12px] p-5`
- Header: title left + "View All" hyperlink right
- Sub-items: `bg-[#fafafa] hover:bg-accent/50 rounded-[8px] p-3`, `gap-3`
- Icon container: `size-10 rounded-[8px] bg-[#e0f5fd]`
- Status text: due = `text-[#ff9d00]`, paid = `text-[#21c179]`

## Consent / Agreement Cards
- Container: `bg-white border border-[#e0e0e0] rounded-[12px] p-6 flex flex-col gap-4`
- No hover effect
- Title: `text-[16px] font-semibold`
- Icon: `size-10 rounded-full` with solid semantic bg, `size-5 text-white` icon
- Checkbox: `size-4 accent-[#004299]`, label `text-[14px]`, `items-center gap-3`
- Links in label: `text-[#00b8f5] font-semibold hover:underline`
- CTA: disabled state `bg-[#e0e0e0] text-[#7e7e7e] cursor-not-allowed`
